It's my husband.

00:27.880 --> 00:28.960
He just collapsed.

00:28.960 --> 00:30.000
And I can't feel him
breathing.

00:30.000 --> 00:31.240
Ma'am, I need you
to step away.

00:31.520 --> 00:32.400
Ma'am, I need
you to step away.

00:32.400 --> 00:33.360
Ma'am, I need you
to step away.

00:33.360 --> 00:35.360
Please help him.
We will do the best
we can.

